metadata.name: Legend of the ancient forest
metadata.description:
Legend of the ancient forest by @ABAElena and @Anasstasiart

Artists: 

https://twitter.com/ABAElena

https://twitter.com/anasstasiart

The legend of the ancient forest says: whoever is lucky enough to meet beautiful fairies and receive a magic flower from them, a happy life awaits him. Fairies live on trees in the deepest thicket, and only a person with a pure heart will find a way there and be able to receive his gift.
